title: [Smuggling Tunnels, Mess Hall]
description: Pots, pans, and other metal dishes scatter across the floor, all covered with a fine layer of dust.  Soup bones and other cooking ingredients rot in the dirt, adding a less than pleasant fragrance to the air.  How one of the plates got halfway imbedded into the ceiling is anyone's guess.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
